      <title>创纪录的 570 亿美元资金流出冲击巴西对冲基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/investors-pull-record-57-billion-from-brazil-hedge-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年，由于利率上升和当地市场的崩溃，投资者以创纪录的速度从巴西对冲基金中撤出资金，导致这个陷入困境的行业连续第二年表现不佳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/investors-pull-record-57-billion-from-brazil-hedge-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 12:01:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
